{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2019, "height": 2813, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [137, 752, 213, 1464], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三八九", "block_bbox": [152, 2134, 205, 2259], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公元一九九五年农历正月初六谷旦", "block_bbox": [403, 246, 1049, 294], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "先母王氏秀英之墓碑", "block_bbox": [403, 379, 795, 424], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公讳王氏秀英，禀赋耿直，为人清正，常以勤学教子、勤俭居身，主吾杜发照、云英、淑卿，先父早殁，吾等尚幼，母操劳家务，含辛茹苦，名闻遐迩，对吾家有不世之功。教子之殷，甚于慈母；督教之严，甚于师褒。出入必检其所携，游息必询其所往，罢读归来必考其所学，以长以教，以至于成。对于吾家之功，秃笔难述，略叙梗概，今值养父三周年之际，勒石墓前，以示美留人寰，永垂不朽。", "block_bbox": [312, 446, 1461, 883], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "孝男发照媳马软巧（以下人名从略）敬立", "block_bbox": [401, 901, 1240, 950], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "女云英婿林森", "block_bbox": [402, 965, 733, 1009], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "淑卿勉成", "block_bbox": [403, 1030, 650, 1073], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一九九八年农历正月十一日谷旦", "block_bbox": [403, 1095, 994, 1138], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "尊先父杜公讳俊英合葬之墓碑母张氏\n", "block_bbox": [406, 1223, 957, 1331], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "2\n", "block_bbox": [1487, 252, 1835, 1228], "block_id": 10, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "先父杜公讳俊英，乳名河云，生于一九一九年正月初五日，卒于一九九八年七月初六日，享寿七旬有九。（父象贤公，葬岭西村柿树园地。）配张氏，生二女；长女淑贞，适西官庄村刘姓；次女焕贞，适偃师县塔庄村李姓。禀赋聪颖，稳重学固，身润德厚，满腹经纶，开口成章，道积厥躬，处事罡直，文明公正。敬老人，乡邻称孝子。民国时曾任校长、连长之职，医术不凡，医德高尚，治病济人何止千万，不索钱财，实为一代名医。中年丧妻，使女不受虐，未再续弦。兄嫂早逝，千辛万苦，呕血付于侄辈成家立业，城乡邻里享有声誉。女侄辈对公养育之恩未报万一，际三周年，略述生平一二，聊表思念，勒石墓前，永存不没。", "block_bbox": [319, 1352, 1834, 1916], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "合养\n\n", "block_bbox": [1471, 1674, 1822, 2576], "block_id": 12, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "男：文忠媳：李曾女女孙男震媳：黄程\n\n张小梅女娟婿：王晓军\n培丽马万伟\n培娟\n\n女：淑贞婿：刘卫国外孙：女刘秋芬婿：陈文安\n刘静\n\n刘楠\n\n焕贞李海曾男李新华\n公元二零零一年农历三月十二日清明\n\n注：载入谱时，改正了几处错字。\n\n", "block_bbox": [411, 1933, 1404, 2562], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 12}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.968224048614502, "coordinate": [312.75079345703125, 446.64886474609375, 1461.463623046875, 883.4469604492188]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9640212059020996, "coordinate": [1487.911376953125, 252.9429931640625, 1835.510986328125, 1228.9049072265625]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9614567160606384, "coordinate": [1471.776123046875, 1674.231201171875, 1822.247314453125, 2576.982666015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8187219500541687, "coordinate": [401.1983642578125, 901.869140625, 1240.39453125, 950.583251953125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7665157318115234, "coordinate": [403.6649169921875, 1095.502197265625, 994.1942138671875, 1138.649658203125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7295313477516174, "coordinate": [416.3753967285156, 2386.83203125, 1134.8245849609375, 2557.6416015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.702914834022522, "coordinate": [319.5780029296875, 1352.628173828125, 1834.5548095703125, 1916.7841796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6912211179733276, "coordina